Package sailpoint.connector

Built in classes used to read and authenticate to enterprise applications.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Connector The Connector interface allows IIQ to authenticate and read data from to enterprise applications.
 

Class Summary
AbstractConnector A base abstract connector that is intended to be extended by all Connector classes.
AbstractFileBasedConnector A class that offers file transport services for File Based Connectors.
CollectorServices A class that offers services that are common for all Connectors and Collectors in IdentityIQ.
DelimitedFileConnector A connector that can be used to read data from one or more delimited text files.
JDBCConnector A connector that can be used to read data from JDBC enabled database engines.
 

Package sailpoint.connector Description

Built in classes used to read and authenticate to enterprise applications. This package is primarily used during aggregation of user and account data. The connector offers three main services authenticate, getObject and iterateObject (list all objects).

NOTE: Not all of the classes in this package are included in this java-doc distribution.

Since:
1.0
